<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-8 columns">
    <h1>Quick Network Setup</h1>
    <hr>
    <h2>Sign Up</h2>
    <p>To get started with Cucumber Tony, head over to <a href="my.ctapp.io">my.ctapp.io</a> and once here, click <b>Sign Up</b>, enter your email address and then click on the <b>Sign-up for free</b> button.</p>
    <div class="text-center">
		<img src="/images/community/documentation/ct-register.gif">
		</div>
    <p>You'll be sent a registration link by email, simply open it up and click on the link, which will start you on your account creation in Cucumber Tony.</p>
		<hr>
		<h2>Your First Location</h2>
		<div class="text-center">
		<img src="/images/community/documentation/first-location.gif">
		</div>
    <p>You will now have to fill in a few bits of information, including things like your Location name and custom brand.</p>
    <p>Just follow the steps in the setup one by one as shown above, until you reach your location dashboard.</p>
